room_title: Escape room "The President's Briefcase" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
review: Doesn't matter if you're new to escape rooms or not. My group did the President's Briefcase. This is the best escape room I've ever done! This sets the standard for all escape rooms. We will be going back for the other rooms for sure!
